→ Read internal/infrastructure/library/validator_test.go [offset=694, limit=40]
I see the issue now. The problem is that FixLibrary first removes missing entries, then checks presets against the modified Resources. So `skill/missing1` becomes a "ghost" after being removed.

The fix is to track which refs were identified as missing files before checking presets. Let me update FixLibrary:
